genresAdvancedInfo.name: tigrigna pop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Tigrigna Pop is a popular music genre originating from Eritrea and Ethiopia. It is characterized by its upbeat tempo, catchy melodies, and use of traditional Tigrigna instruments. The lyrics often revolve around love, relationships, and social issues, and are sung in the Tigrigna language.
